Cool language scanner

Nikki DelRosso
CIS 461 - Intro to Compiler Construction
Spring 2013

Usage: ./scanner [FILE_INPUT]

Contents:
	src/ - Contains source code
		ply/       - PLY library

		error.py   - Contains exceptions for error handling.  Includes the calculation
		             of columns for error reporting.

		lexer.py   - Contains lexing rules, token definitions, and a list of "Extended
		             Cool" reserved words.

		scanner.py - The driver; handles file reading, the token loop, and detects 
		             and displays errors.
		

